title: Its Me O Lord - Autobiography of Rockwell Kent (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Dodd, Mead | 1955 | Pdf | Eng | 617 p | 101 MB

it's me o lord is an autobiography such as perhaps no other man of our time could have written. For what other contemporary has encompassed within the span of his life the multifarious qualities of painter, writer, explorer, illustrator, farmer, sailor, book designer, architect, carpenter, orator, lithographer, wood engraver, pamphleteer and political figure?
If Rockwell Kent is already something of a legend, it is because his exploits and accomplishments are of legendary proportions.
In this magnificent book, which contains nearly one hundred new illustrations by him and more than two hundred reproductions of his previous works, Rockwell Kent tells the full story of his fabulous life
